309
00:22:57,355 --> 00:23:02,456
{\an5}<i>(Ashura)</i>
<i>That tree is a remnant of the</i>
<i>specter that almost destroyed</i>
<i>our entire world.</i>

310
00:23:02,489 --> 00:23:06,656
{\an1}<i>I've been ordered to do</i>
<i>something about it.</i>

311
00:23:06,690 --> 00:23:11,557
{\an1}<i>The power of the Divine Tree is</i>
<i>indeed making this land</i>
<i>fruitful,... but...</i>

312
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:14,692
{\an1}<i>it's also making the</i>
<i>villagers ill.</i>

313
00:23:14,725 --> 00:23:19,325
<i>(Hagoromo)</i>
<i>Next time on Naruto Shippuden:</i>
<i>"Ashura's Decision."</i>

